item.title: Safezones help!
item.dc:creator: @tonypker13 tonypker13
item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

No need for admin. Ill help.
First go to the SOUTHWEST corner of the safezone area your making.
The first number you have, the 3382, replace it with your 1st coord. Replace the 9758 with the 2nd coord on the SOUTHWEST corner.
Now go to the NORTHEAST corner and repeat.
Re-Cap.
1st and 3rd number set = 1st and 2nd coord on SOUTHWEST corner.
2nd and 4th number set = 2nd and 4th coord on NORTHEAST corner.
